subject: America's Cup
Sailboats and Sailing
Suits and Litigation
organizations: San Franciscos Golden Gate Yacht Club
lead_paragraph: San Francisco’s Golden Gate Yacht Club announced that it and the vanquished trustee Societe Nautique de Genève had agreed to drop their remaining legal actions against each other.
